7.9.19 ‘append:SOURCE,TARGET’
-----------------------------

Works the same way as ‘insert:’ -- takes the value from SOURCE and adds
it to TARGET.  Both ‘insert:’ and ‘append:’ add new rows to list and
tree widgets and set text in entry and edit widgets.


